    {
      "id": "bc402608-6d13-4e34-a011-35b19f761ab4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use augmented reality to assist visualize 3D models in an architecture course. Collaborative behaviors with this system seem to improve student outcomes. Authors perform an experiment where they test the students, do an Augmented Reality Experiment and then are tested again.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "bc402608-6d13-4e34-a011-35b19f761ab4",
